data.name: 0000 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: That reminds me of something Nagato said.

data.name: 0001 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: That she'll cooperate if we're ever troubled by anything.

data.name: 0002 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What are you talking about?

data.name: 0003 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Isn't that obvious? She's a fellow member of the SOS Brigade, you know?

data.name: 0004 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well that's the way you see it.

data.name: 0005 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But to me, hearing those words coming from Nagato meant a lot.

data.name: 0006 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: But Nagato was never originally from the SOS Brigade--she's from the literature club?

data.name: 0007 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You stole not only her, but her clubroom as well.

data.name: 0008 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: She has every right to hold a grudge against us.

data.name: 0009 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What are you talking about, Kyon?

data.name: 0010 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Yuki even said she's happy to join the SOS Brigade, and for us to use the clubroom.

data.name: 0011 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You were there at the time. You didn't forget, did you?

data.name: 0012 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: She probably felt pressured by your menacing expression...

data.name: 0013 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: ...and said so feeling like she didn't have a choice.

data.name: 0014 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: If someone doesn't want something they'd usually just say so.

data.name: 0015 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well, you would surely rather die than reluctantly consent for something you don't want.

data.name: 0016 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But don't assume the rest of the world's humans are all the same as you.

data.name: 0017 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I'm jealous you can so easily do so.

data.name: 0018 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What the heck? That doesn't feel like a compliment.

data.name: 0019 (283.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Naturally. That's because it's not a compliment.

data.name: 0020 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: …Look, let's just go--!

data.name: 0021 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi remembered she was standing still and began to rapidly advance.

data.name: 0022 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Seeing her back storming away, I thought--

data.name: 0023 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I suppose--Haruhi--I don't know about at first, but...

data.name: 0024 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: ...it looks to me like Nagato wants to be together with us by her own accord now.

data.name: 0025 (283.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …She's probably enjoying it in her own Nagato way.

data.name: 0026 (283.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Um, Suzumiya. About Nagato…

data.name: 0027 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What's this about Yuki?

data.name: 0028 (283.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Well, it's just that Nagato is a literature club member, right?

data.name: 0029 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Well, I suppose technically.

data.name: 0030 (283.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Does that mean she's not really an SOS Brigade member...?

data.name: 0031 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You're asking that now of all times? Of course Yuki is an SOS Brigade member.

data.name: 0032 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Sure, according to documents she may be a literature club member―

data.name: 0033 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: But after all she's done for us, there's no doubt anymore.

data.name: 0034 (283.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: R-right…

data.name: 0035 (283.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: …Who's there?

data.name: 0036 (283.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: I will eliminate those who attempt to interfere with Haruhi Suzumiya outside regulations.

data.name: 0038 (283.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Irregular intervention is undesirable for the cause of observing Haruhi Suzumiya.

data.name: 0039 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Yuki, what's up--standing still like that?

data.name: 0040 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Why are you holding a fire extinguisher?

data.name: 0041 (283.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: We were attacked so I made them submit.

data.name: 0042 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Phah--What's that, Yuki--Is that supposed to be some kind of gag?

data.name: 0043 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It's not like you to pull gags... I'll have to tell the others later.

data.name: 0045 (283.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Nagato is rather mysterious, don't you think? Always like a silent observer.

data.name: 0046 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What's this all of a sudden, Koizumi?

data.name: 0047 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I guess you're right, but Yuki is fine as she is. It would be weird if she talked a lot.

data.name: 0048 (283.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Oh I see, that... might just be right now I that I consider it.

data.name: 0049 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It is. It makes you laugh just thinking about it, right?

data.name: 0050 (283.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: #P06I wonder if Nagato's character is the result of your desire after all...?

data.name: 0051 (283.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hm, Koizumi--Did you say something?

data.name: 0052 (283.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Ah nothing, I was just talking to myself.
